uveau champs d&rsquo;actions avec <strong>la sant\u00e9 des femmes<\/strong>, dans des pays o\u00f9 elle est souvent ignor\u00e9e\u2026<\/p>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full is-style-default\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1000\" height=\"1000\" src=\"https:\/\/www.amtm.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/0Appel-Sante.gif\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-6543\"\/><\/figure>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center has-vivid-cyan-blue-color has-text-color has-large-font-size\">Dites \u00ab\u00a0Oui\u00a0\u00bb \u00e0 la sant\u00e9 d&rsquo;abord !<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center\">Gr\u00e2ce \u00e0 votre aide, des milliers de personnes pourront \u00eatre soign\u00e9es dans les ann\u00e9es qui viennent.<br>Des vies seront sauv\u00e9es !<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center has-black-color has-text-color has-medium-font-size\"><strong><a href=\"https:\/\/secure.payzen.eu\/vads-site\/DONS_EN_LIGNE_AMTM\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Faites un don en ligne, en cliquant ICI<\/a><\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center\">et en cochant la case \u00ab&nbsp;Appel Sant\u00e9 \u00bb<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center has-black-color has-text-color has-medium-font-size\"><strong><a href=\"https:\/\/www.amtm.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/Appel-Sante.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Ou faites un ch\u00e8que<\/a><\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center\">\u00e0 l\u2019ordre d\u2019AMTM au pr\u00e9cisant au dos \u00ab Appel Sant\u00e9 \u00bb ou a envoyer avec <a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https:\/\/www.amtm.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/Appel-Sante.pdf\" target=\"_blank\">le formulaire \u00e0 t\u00e9l\u00e9charger ici<\/a><br>\u00e0 AMTM \u2013 81 av Mar\u00e9chal Joffre 92000 Nanterre<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\">\n<figure cl